  "title": "Part Time Freelancer Accounts cum Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>· Candidate must possess</p><p>at least O/A Level/Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.</p><p>· No working experience in the related field is required for this position.</p><p><br /></p><p>· Required Skill(s): Good PC skills and familiar with Microsoft Office</p><p>· Preferably Junior Executive specialized in Finance - General/Cost Accounting or equivalent</p><p><br /></p><p>· Be Independent, meticulous and able to work under pressure</p><p>· Possess a willing to learn and proactive attitude</p><p>· Training on work-related knowledge and competencies provided</p><p>· Bilingual</p><p><br /></p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Handle full sets of clients' accounts</li><li>Support Accounts Team</li><li>Handle corporate tax admin/employment pass admin</li><li>Maintenance of proper records and filing system;</li><li>Support operations and general day-to-day administrative duties;</li><li>Provide secretarial support to Team leader;</li><li>Able to handle confidential information in a professional manner;</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned;</li><li>Able to work independently and as a team;</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>We provide on-the-job training</strong></p><p><strong>We provide opportunities for career advancement within company</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>This role is offered on a freelance/ independent contractor basis. Working hours are flexible.</strong><br /></p>",
